additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: WARNING: DO NOT SPRAY NEAR A NAKED FLAME OR ANY HOT SURFACE. KEEP AWAY FROM SOURCES OF IGNITION - NO SMOKING. AVOID DIRECT INHALATION. USE IN WELL VENTILATED PLACES. AVOID PROLONGED SPRAYING. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. Caution: Pressurised Dispenser. Protect From Sunlight And Do Not Expose To Temperatures Exceeding 50C. Do Not Pierce Or Burn, Even When Empty. Intentional Misuse By Deliberately Concentrating And Inhaling Contents May Be Harmful Or Fatal.
